title: @troyesivan #DreamTrackAI a love song about my dog Matty and his treats
transcript: - So if Troye Sivan made a love song about my dog, Maddy, and his favorite treats, what do you guys think that would sound like? Using the new Dream Track Experiment in YouTube Shorts with a simple prompt, you can choose your desired artist and get a fully custed AI-generated song almost instantly. Listen to this. Matty, my dog You are so sweet You are so good I love you And when you're hungry I gave you treats 'Cause you deserve them I love you I don't know, I think Troye has another hit on his hands here.
